node.text:
📣 Attention please! 😸 Wilfred will be closing his shop in A WEEK! This is your last chance to own Wilfred Warrior merchandise! Wilfred's shop can be found in the link in bio. Or Google it.

Background: We made Wilfred's shop in 2019 when Wilfred's popularity suddenly went into the stratosphere and demand for his face on stuff was high. We had no experience whatsoever of producing merchandise, but seeing Wilfred's image used illegitimately all over Amazon, Redbubble, etc gave us a push to step up to the plate! With this type of merchandise profit margins are very low. Some products literally just break even and we put them there only for fans' enjoyment. Unfortunately due to the costs of running the shop it is not unusual to go into minus. In order to make money with this kind of merchandise you need to advertise a lot. Advertising always brought us an influx of sales, but we have never been keen on doing lots of advertising on Wilfred's page. Especially since we don't post generally too much! Maybe we will look at alternatives for providing official Wilfred merchandise again, but for now, we wanted to give you all a heads up for those of you who might have been planning presents, or who have always planned to get something but never got round to it. And to everyone who did buy Wilfred's merchandise, Thank you for your support! It always put smiles on our faces when we saw pictures of Wilfred's fans in his merchandise 😸
